---
import { FREEPHONE_NUMBER } from '../../../../../utils/constants';

interface Props {
	location: string;
	locationTel: string;
}

const { location, locationTel } = Astro.props;
---

<h2 class="h3">
	Do you have a Blocked Sink or Toilet and live in {location} or the surrounding area?
</h2>
<h3 class="h4 coloured-text">
	Call us now on {
		locationTel ? locationTel : `Freephone ${FREEPHONE_NUMBER} - 24 hour Emergency Helpline`
	}
</h3>

<p>
	When you suspect a blockage, knowing what signs to look out for is the first step to a <strong
		>quick resolution</strong
	>. Is there a foul smell emitting from your sink or bath? Perhaps the water is taking a long time
	to drain?
</p>
<p>
	We are <strong>plumbing and drainage specialists</strong> with a wealth of experience tackling blocked
	sinks, basins, toilets and pipework.
</p>
<h3 class="h4 coloured-text">
	Call us today and find out why we're one of the highest rated companies for clearing blocked sinks
	and toilets in {location}.
</h3>
